snippet.title: WHAT THE GOLF? Launch Trailer - Out now Apple Arcade and PC!
snippet.description:
The golf game for people who hate golf!
Made by people who know nothing about golf!
PC: http://whatthegolf.com/pc
Apple: http://whatthegolf.com/apple
Nintendo Switch: https://whatthegolf.com/switchstore

You wouldn't golf a car!

What the critics wrote:
"'What the Golf' Is WarioWare With Frickin' Golf Clubs" - Vice 
'"WHAT THE GOLF? is the perfect game for people who don't care about golf" - Engadget 
"WHAT THE GOLF? is the first Apple Arcade subscription game I finished, and it's because I couldn't put it down" - Vandal
